snippet.title: Sonic Triple Trouble 16-bit - Release Date Revealed! (fan game)
snippet.description:
Sonic Triple Trouble 16-bit is a fan game for free and for fun!
|| DOWNLOAD DEMO: https://gamejolt.com/games/sonictripletrouble16bit/322794
|| FOLLOW TWITTER FOR UPDATES: https://twitter.com/NoahNCopeland

This is an unofficial fan game, and will NOT be monetized. 
This is not affiliated with SEGA or Sonic Team. It's a passion project.

art by AeroArtwork https://twitter.com/AeroArtwork
3D by wolforam https://twitter.com/wolforamc4d
